Please do not controll other charaters in the future, Cyberwolf. I'll let 
this pass, but be more careful.

::Kluster::

Kluster looks from Phobia to Savanah. "I am Kluster, commander of the Maximal 
battle cruiser The Cybertronian Fire. These two are also Maximals, Hysteria 
and Blur."

He turns around, motioning all four of the bots behind him to follow. "Let's 
get back to my ship. We can talk there."
